# [Interview #235: KOD Signing Report - Kevin Dean, Entry #17](https://www.theoryland.com/intvmain.php?i=235#17)

#### Kevin Dean

At this point, got kind of chaotic. I stood where I had been seated, and listed to a lot of what RJ was saying, but I really didn't hear much. I heard him say that only Philadelphia had sunshine, all of his other signings has been in the rain.
